WEBVTT

00:00:03.203 --> 00:00:05.138
[NARRATOR] Gold Roger,
the King of the Pirates,

00:00:05.171 --> 00:00:08.108
attained every treasure that
the world had to offer.

00:00:08.141 --> 00:00:10.844
Smiling, even as he
stood upon the scaffold,

00:00:10.877 --> 00:00:13.146
he issued a challenge
to the world.

00:00:13.179 --> 00:00:14.381
[GOLD ROGER]
You want my treasure?

00:00:14.414 --> 00:00:15.482
You can have it!

00:00:15.515 --> 00:00:18.351
I left everything I gathered
together in one place.

00:00:18.385 --> 00:00:20.620
Now you just have to find it!

00:00:20.653 --> 00:00:23.757
[NARRATOR] Now, those who dare
to dream hoist their flags

00:00:23.790 --> 00:00:26.693
and sail into
the Great Pirate Era!

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:34.854
[NARRATOR] All pirates searching
for the treasure One Piece

00:02:35.155 --> 00:02:38.024
must brave the second
half of the Grand Line.

00:02:38.057 --> 00:02:42.695
These wild and dangerous seas
are known as the New World.

00:02:42.729 --> 00:02:45.798
Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy
whose body became rubber

00:02:45.832 --> 00:02:47.367
after eating the Gum Gum Fruit,

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:51.070
sets sail into the New World
with his faithful crew.

00:02:51.104 --> 00:02:55.208
I'm gonna be the
King of the Pirates!

00:02:57.877 --> 00:02:59.512
[NARRATOR] The first stop
on Luffy's journey is

00:02:59.546 --> 00:03:02.282
Fishman Island, thousands
of feet below sea level,

00:03:02.315 --> 00:03:05.151
where his crew becomes
involved in a civil war.

00:03:05.185 --> 00:03:07.487
The Fishman Pirates,
led by Hordy Jones

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:12.759
and assisted by Vander Decken,
plot to overthrow King Neptune.

00:03:12.792 --> 00:03:15.495
The enemy captures
Zoro, Usopp, and Brook,

00:03:15.528 --> 00:03:17.564
trapping them at
the Ryugu Palace

00:03:17.597 --> 00:03:20.333
while the other Straw Hats
meet in the Sea Forest.

00:03:21.834 --> 00:03:24.604
[LUFFY] Get outta my way.
I gotta go save my friends!

00:03:24.637 --> 00:03:26.906
And when I'm done,
I'm kicking Hordy's ass!

00:03:26.940 --> 00:03:29.909
I told you not to
get involved with him!

00:03:32.679 --> 00:03:34.547
[LUFFY] "Something Has
Happened to Hordy!

00:03:34.581 --> 00:03:37.150
The True Power
of the Evil Drug!"

00:03:39.886 --> 00:03:41.120
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE AA]
It's time to show

00:03:41.154 --> 00:03:42.855
the island who's boss!

00:03:42.889 --> 00:03:43.890
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE BB]
That's right!

00:03:43.923 --> 00:03:45.858
All we gotta do
is kill the king.

00:03:45.892 --> 00:03:49.195
Once that's done, the royal
army'll surrender fast!

00:03:49.229 --> 00:03:52.632
And if Neptune's dead, Fishman
Island's gonna need a new ruler!

00:03:52.665 --> 00:03:55.168
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE B chuckles]
I can't wait!

00:03:56.703 --> 00:04:01.708
[chuckling]

00:04:07.914 --> 00:04:10.149
[NARRATOR]
Meanwhile, at Candy Factory Town

00:04:10.183 --> 00:04:12.185
in the center of the island.

00:04:16.889 --> 00:04:20.460
Boss Daruma? Hey, you okay?

00:04:20.493 --> 00:04:22.629
He's chewing right through
the factory walls!

00:04:22.662 --> 00:04:24.697
Yeah, like it was nothing!

00:04:32.572 --> 00:04:38.011
[FISHMEN yelling]

00:04:39.145 --> 00:04:42.315
My fangs itch for more! [laughs]

00:04:42.348 --> 00:04:43.383
Huh?

00:04:45.418 --> 00:04:46.552
What's this crap?

00:04:46.586 --> 00:04:48.755
I don't want some trendy
cappuccino latte thing

00:04:48.788 --> 00:04:50.490
or fancy sponge cake
when I'm hungry!

00:04:50.523 --> 00:04:52.058
That junk's not real food!

00:04:52.091 --> 00:04:53.960
What in the hell do I look like?

00:04:53.993 --> 00:04:56.496
I-I'm sorry, Boss!
I'll get something else!

00:04:56.529 --> 00:04:57.964
That's good,
because you're starting

00:04:57.997 --> 00:04:59.532
to look pretty tasty yourself!

00:04:59.565 --> 00:05:03.670
For a snack, I like fish bones
and I like 'em big! Now go!

00:05:04.771 --> 00:05:07.407
Uh, sure thing!
Big fish bones, I got it!

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:10.743
Nevermind. I'm gonna go whet
my appetite on some soldiers

00:05:10.777 --> 00:05:13.112
and maybe the royal family, too!

00:05:13.146 --> 00:05:16.582
I guess I'll see the rest of
you bums at Conchcorde Plaza!

00:05:16.616 --> 00:05:19.552
Don't you dare be late!
We all have to be there!

00:05:19.585 --> 00:05:21.454
What should we do
about the citizens?

00:05:21.487 --> 00:05:22.689
Come on.

00:05:22.722 --> 00:05:25.892
Did you morons pay attention
to a word Captain Hordy said?

00:05:25.925 --> 00:05:29.028
He told us, "No more
stepping on her picture."

00:05:29.062 --> 00:05:31.631
[laughs] Leave 'em
alone for now!

00:05:31.664 --> 00:05:34.434
Those losers'll get what's
coming to them soon enough!

00:05:34.467 --> 00:05:36.002
[DARUMA laughs]

00:05:42.442 --> 00:05:46.512
[FISHMEN murmuring]

00:05:46.546 --> 00:05:49.882
[FISHMEN gasping]

00:05:49.916 --> 00:05:52.385
How are we supposed to
stand up to these guys?

00:05:52.418 --> 00:05:54.821
Including Hordy,
the New Fishman Pirates have

00:05:54.854 --> 00:05:59.859
four shark Fishmen as officers,
and a giant squid Fishman.

00:05:59.892 --> 00:06:02.829
Not to mention their bodyguard
is a blue-ringed octopus merman

00:06:02.862 --> 00:06:05.898
known as the best swordsman
on the entire island!

00:06:05.932 --> 00:06:11.037
I think the Neptune brothers are
the only hope we've got left.

00:06:11.070 --> 00:06:14.674
Then all we can do
is keep the faith.

00:06:16.142 --> 00:06:17.377
Pu-wink.

00:06:17.410 --> 00:06:21.347
[NARRATOR] At Waterwheel Town
in the island's northern region.

00:06:21.381 --> 00:06:22.448
[FISHMAN E]
Did you hear?

00:06:22.482 --> 00:06:24.350
The Princes are making their
way to Conchcorde Plaza!

00:06:24.384 --> 00:06:26.352
[FISHMAN F]
This country's in such a mess!

00:06:26.386 --> 00:06:28.388
Tell me about it.
All we wanted to do

00:06:28.421 --> 00:06:30.556
was improve our relationship
with the humans.

00:06:30.590 --> 00:06:31.924
There's no reason to
threaten everyone

00:06:31.958 --> 00:06:34.060
with death like
some kind of madman!

00:06:34.093 --> 00:06:37.263
And on top of those threats,
they wanna execute the king.

00:06:37.296 --> 00:06:39.499
Maybe Hordy will be willing
to bargain with us.

00:06:39.532 --> 00:06:42.602
After all, we've got
his men held hostage.

00:06:42.635 --> 00:06:44.237
Held hostage?

00:06:45.805 --> 00:06:47.573
Your plan isn't going to work.

00:06:47.607 --> 00:06:50.943
Boss Hordy would rather you
cut us downsun than negotiate.

00:06:50.977 --> 00:06:53.679
He's more ruthless than
the other Fishman Pirates.

00:06:53.713 --> 00:06:56.315
It's why he looks
downsun on the rest of us.

00:06:58.184 --> 00:06:59.652
This can't be good.

00:06:59.685 --> 00:07:01.320
Ever since the
princes defeated him,

00:07:01.354 --> 00:07:04.190
Officer Dosun's power level
has dropped to "downsun."

00:07:04.223 --> 00:07:05.958
Now he's just weak and gloomy.

00:07:05.992 --> 00:07:08.060
[FISHMAN PIRATE GG] Lemme
give him an Energy Steroid.

00:07:09.729 --> 00:07:12.064
[DOSUN] Thinking about
it just brings me downsun.

00:07:12.098 --> 00:07:13.599
It's depressing!

00:07:17.003 --> 00:07:19.338
[DOSUN grunts]

00:07:19.372 --> 00:07:22.275
Sometimes Hordy
makes me frownsun.

00:07:24.444 --> 00:07:26.212
Huh?

00:07:26.245 --> 00:07:29.415
Hordy doesn't like Fishmen who
do business with human pirates.

00:07:29.449 --> 00:07:33.553
He'll give them the
bumpsun without mercy.

00:07:33.586 --> 00:07:35.188
[FISHWOMAN A]
"Bumpsun"?

00:07:35.221 --> 00:07:37.390
[DOSUN] All those Fishmen
who donated their blood

00:07:37.423 --> 00:07:39.725
to help out wounded humans--

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:43.062
he gave them the old whumpsun
in the dark of night.

00:07:44.096 --> 00:07:45.731
[FISHMAN H]
"Whumpsun"?

00:07:45.765 --> 00:07:49.101
Hordy believes that human
blood is naturally tainted,

00:07:49.135 --> 00:07:52.872
and whenever we receive their
blood or offer them our own,

00:07:52.905 --> 00:07:56.209
we dosun our pure
blood a disservice!

00:07:56.242 --> 00:07:58.377
He's back to saying "dosun" now!

00:07:58.411 --> 00:08:00.313
[DOSUN]
Any Fishman who supports humans

00:08:00.346 --> 00:08:03.316
is a traitor and
needs to be punished!

00:08:03.349 --> 00:08:07.920
Our people will never be able
to advance with them in our way!

00:08:07.954 --> 00:08:10.256
All right, that's enough!

00:08:10.289 --> 00:08:13.693
I'm gonna go whamsun on you!

00:08:13.726 --> 00:08:15.728
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
He's higher than "dosun"!

00:08:15.761 --> 00:08:18.397
[FISHMAN AA]
The chains are shattered!

00:08:18.431 --> 00:08:20.032
You bastard!

00:08:20.066 --> 00:08:23.002
[DOSUN yells]

00:08:23.035 --> 00:08:25.638
[AMMO KNIGHTS scream]

00:08:25.671 --> 00:08:27.473
[FISHMAN I] He knocked
them out with one swing!

00:08:27.507 --> 00:08:31.978
Fukaboshi! I'll get
you back with a slamsun!

00:08:32.011 --> 00:08:33.045
[FISHMEN shouting]

00:08:33.079 --> 00:08:38.551
Then I'll smash your face
with a big fat boomsun!

00:08:38.584 --> 00:08:41.087
[DOSUN yelling]

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:45.925
[FISHMEN shouting]

00:08:45.958 --> 00:08:49.228
My enemies will face doomsun!

00:08:49.262 --> 00:08:53.566
Head to the Conchcorde Plaza
for the execution! Let's move!

00:08:53.599 --> 00:08:55.635
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
Yeah!

00:08:59.238 --> 00:09:00.773
[NARRATOR]
At the south part of the island

00:09:00.806 --> 00:09:03.242
in front of the
Fishman Cultural Hall.

00:09:04.243 --> 00:09:05.945
[HYOUZOU sighs]

00:09:05.978 --> 00:09:09.348
Huh? Who are you callin' drunk?
Oh, yeah, that's right, it's me.

00:09:09.382 --> 00:09:11.217
This isn't funny anymore, Boss!

00:09:11.250 --> 00:09:14.353
Pull yourself together! You're
in no shape to fight like that!

00:09:14.387 --> 00:09:16.722
I think you worry too much, pal!

00:09:16.756 --> 00:09:19.492
Relax, drinks are on
the house! It's my treat!

00:09:19.525 --> 00:09:21.294
That's not important right now!

00:09:21.327 --> 00:09:24.230
Fukaboshi is leading Neptune's
army into the plaza!

00:09:24.263 --> 00:09:25.932
We have to be ready for them!

00:09:25.965 --> 00:09:27.667
Even worse, if things go bad,

00:09:27.700 --> 00:09:30.269
Jimbei might even
show up to fight!

00:09:30.303 --> 00:09:32.371
This isn't a joke, Boss!

00:09:33.639 --> 00:09:37.944
It's no use. He's weak as a sea
cucumber and just as slippery.

00:09:37.977 --> 00:09:40.613
Huh? Well, I'll be!

00:09:40.646 --> 00:09:43.849
How'd you get your head
spinnin' around like that?

00:09:43.883 --> 00:09:46.352
I'm standing still!
How drunk are you?

00:09:46.385 --> 00:09:49.488
This is awful. I doubt
Hyouzou can even hold his sword.

00:09:49.522 --> 00:09:51.824
[HYOUZOU]
Pfft, sure I can!

00:09:51.857 --> 00:09:53.859
Get away from him immediately!

00:09:53.893 --> 00:09:55.328
I'm serious!

00:09:55.361 --> 00:09:56.862
Hyouzou will slice into anyone

00:09:56.896 --> 00:09:58.631
and everyone when
he's this drunk!

00:09:58.664 --> 00:10:00.166
Make a run for it!

00:10:00.199 --> 00:10:02.602
He'll slice anyone?

00:10:06.772 --> 00:10:09.508
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES groan]

00:10:09.542 --> 00:10:11.077
He attacked his own guys?

00:10:11.110 --> 00:10:13.312
[HYOUZOU chuckles]

00:10:13.346 --> 00:10:14.847
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
Huh?

00:10:16.616 --> 00:10:19.652
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES scream]

00:10:34.166 --> 00:10:36.535
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES gasping]

00:10:36.569 --> 00:10:43.242
See? I can fight just
fine. Right, boys?

00:10:43.275 --> 00:10:46.078
[HYOUZOU chuckles]

00:10:46.112 --> 00:10:47.146
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES gasp]

00:10:47.179 --> 00:10:50.116
Uh, hey, Hyouzou!
Why don't you go to the plaza?

00:10:50.149 --> 00:10:53.653
There you can cut up the royal
family as much as you want! Huh?

00:10:53.686 --> 00:10:57.356
[HYOUZOU]
I, uh... no... wh-- Uh...

00:10:57.390 --> 00:10:58.224
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
Wha--

00:10:58.257 --> 00:11:00.159
What is that even
supposed to mean?

00:11:00.192 --> 00:11:02.495
[ZEO chuckles]

00:11:02.528 --> 00:11:04.230
[NARRATOR]
At the Marine Shopping Mall

00:11:04.263 --> 00:11:06.399
in the east part of the island.

00:11:06.432 --> 00:11:07.900
[FISHMAN J]
We're former soldiers of Neptune

00:11:07.933 --> 00:11:09.035
and proud of it!

00:11:09.068 --> 00:11:12.171
You won't take this country
as long as we're around!

00:11:12.204 --> 00:11:14.407
[FISHMAN J yelling]

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:16.575
Huh? What? Where'd he go?

00:11:16.609 --> 00:11:18.010
[FISHMAN J groaning]

00:11:18.044 --> 00:11:20.346
[FISHMEN groaning]

00:11:20.379 --> 00:11:21.647
Where is he?

00:11:23.416 --> 00:11:25.351
[FISHMAN N gasps, groans]

00:11:25.384 --> 00:11:26.886
[FISHMAN O]
Hold still!

00:11:26.919 --> 00:11:28.621
He disappeared again!

00:11:28.654 --> 00:11:30.856
Damn it, did anyone
see where he went?

00:11:31.991 --> 00:11:32.958
[FISHMAN P groans]

00:11:32.992 --> 00:11:34.427
[FISHMAN O groans]

00:11:35.728 --> 00:11:38.397
[ZEO] You think you pathetic
civilians stand a chance?

00:11:38.431 --> 00:11:40.266
You're dumber than I thought.

00:11:40.299 --> 00:11:42.702
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE K] Heh!
Boss Zeo can blend in perfectly

00:11:42.735 --> 00:11:45.137
with his surroundings
to camouflage himself.

00:11:45.171 --> 00:11:47.273
Just like a chameleon!

00:11:47.306 --> 00:11:48.674
He might be on our side,

00:11:48.708 --> 00:11:51.143
but even we have trouble
figuring out where he is!

00:11:51.177 --> 00:11:52.912
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE K chuckles]

00:11:52.945 --> 00:11:54.213
What? This is unfair!

00:11:54.246 --> 00:11:56.782
How are we supposed to fight
someone we can't even see?

00:11:56.816 --> 00:11:58.284
[ZEO]
You might as well start begging

00:11:58.317 --> 00:12:01.620
for the Neptune Brothers
to bail you out.

00:12:01.654 --> 00:12:03.723
Without them, you're finished.

00:12:03.756 --> 00:12:04.957
[FISHMAN R yelps]

00:12:04.990 --> 00:12:08.060
[ZEO] Though frankly, don't
expect them to last long either.

00:12:08.094 --> 00:12:10.963
Oh, well. Time to
finish you off.

00:12:10.996 --> 00:12:12.698
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE L]
Whoa! A roach!

00:12:12.732 --> 00:12:13.666
Hurry up! Kill it!

00:12:13.699 --> 00:12:18.704
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES grunting]

00:12:27.613 --> 00:12:30.716
That was weird. All of
a sudden, he stopped talking.

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:33.486
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE K]
Did we get it? Is it dead?

00:12:33.519 --> 00:12:35.521
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE L]
Yeah. We got it.

00:12:36.355 --> 00:12:37.590
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
Huh?

00:12:39.792 --> 00:12:42.194
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES gasp]

00:12:42.228 --> 00:12:45.431
[ZEO]
You fools have nowhere to run.

00:12:45.464 --> 00:12:48.801
It's only a matter of time
before we hunt you all down.

00:12:48.834 --> 00:12:51.070
There's no escaping our wrath!

00:12:51.103 --> 00:12:52.805
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE K] He's
talking like nothing happened!

00:12:52.838 --> 00:12:55.274
We just beat him to
a pulp! What class!

00:12:55.307 --> 00:12:56.842
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE L]
No wonder he's called the Noble

00:12:56.876 --> 00:12:58.677
of the Fishman District!

00:12:58.711 --> 00:13:01.046
[ZEO]
Prepare for the revolution.

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:04.917
Later on today
at Conchcorde Plaza...

00:13:06.619 --> 00:13:11.457
[ZEO] ...the Neptune family will
die, and a new king will rise.

00:13:11.490 --> 00:13:14.260
Now, let's head
to the execution!

00:13:14.293 --> 00:13:16.529
[ZEO coughs]

00:13:16.562 --> 00:13:19.298
[HORDY groans]

00:13:19.331 --> 00:13:22.434
What's wrong, Captain?
You're not hurt, are you?

00:13:22.468 --> 00:13:23.869
Don't worry about it.

00:13:23.903 --> 00:13:25.037
You sure?

00:13:25.070 --> 00:13:28.707
I'm fine! Just bring me more
pills! As many as we have!

00:13:28.741 --> 00:13:32.511
But that could kill you! [gasps]

00:13:32.545 --> 00:13:33.512
We want you to get better,

00:13:33.546 --> 00:13:35.481
but taking more pills
is not the way!

00:13:35.514 --> 00:13:37.883
You're already way over
the limit, Boss!

00:13:37.917 --> 00:13:42.087
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES murmuring]

00:13:42.121 --> 00:13:43.956
Want your head crushed in?

00:13:43.989 --> 00:13:46.859
Then fall back in
line and shut up!

00:13:46.892 --> 00:13:48.828
Captain! There's
no need for this!

00:13:48.861 --> 00:13:50.796
We already have
King Neptune hostage!

00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:54.133
Victory's right in front of us!
Just give your body a rest!

00:13:54.166 --> 00:13:57.102
Listen to us! You're
pushing yourself too hard!

00:14:01.941 --> 00:14:03.275
[HORDY grunts]

00:14:06.145 --> 00:14:13.285
[HORDY groaning]

00:14:31.437 --> 00:14:34.673
Get out of the way, Jimbei!
I don't have time for this!

00:14:34.707 --> 00:14:35.875
I will not!

00:14:35.908 --> 00:14:38.611
Fishman problems should
be handled by Fishmen!

00:14:38.644 --> 00:14:39.712
There is no reason why

00:14:39.745 --> 00:14:42.181
this should be so difficult
for you to understand!

00:14:42.214 --> 00:14:44.850
[LUFFY] Shut up! I don't
give a damn about the beef

00:14:44.884 --> 00:14:46.352
the Fishmen and humans have!

00:14:46.385 --> 00:14:48.888
Especially not when my
friends are in danger!

00:14:48.921 --> 00:14:50.623
[JIMBEI]
I can rescue your friends!

00:14:50.656 --> 00:14:53.525
Your interference will
do more harm than good!

00:14:53.559 --> 00:14:55.828
[JIMBEI, LUFFY grunt]

00:14:55.861 --> 00:14:59.398
They both wanna help out,
so why are they arguing so much?

00:14:59.431 --> 00:15:01.533
Their fighting
isn't doing any good!

00:15:01.567 --> 00:15:05.971
[BOTH grunting]

00:15:07.873 --> 00:15:10.576
[FUKABOSHI] How much longer
before we arrive at the plaza?

00:15:10.609 --> 00:15:12.912
[AMMO KNIGHT C]
Less than an hour, sir!

00:15:12.945 --> 00:15:14.780
[AMMO KNIGHT A] Executing
the king at Conchcorde Plaza

00:15:14.813 --> 00:15:18.350
feels calculated. Why not
just do it at the palace?

00:15:18.384 --> 00:15:21.754
I think Hordy might be trying
to lure you princes into a trap!

00:15:21.787 --> 00:15:24.023
That is no concern to me.

00:15:24.056 --> 00:15:25.691
I look forward to this fight.

00:15:25.724 --> 00:15:28.227
I will not let them
murder our father!

00:15:28.260 --> 00:15:30.629
And I refuse to let our
citizens' hearts and minds

00:15:30.663 --> 00:15:33.098
become closed off after
all we've worked for!

00:15:33.132 --> 00:15:35.367
Jimbei kept Hordy
under his watchful eye,

00:15:35.401 --> 00:15:38.404
and now I see that we should
have taken note of that.

00:15:38.437 --> 00:15:40.172
He's probably the
reason human pirates

00:15:40.205 --> 00:15:41.607
have stopped coming
here as well--

00:15:41.640 --> 00:15:43.776
an issue we should have
investigated sooner.

00:15:43.809 --> 00:15:47.012
Say, do you think Shirahoshi is
still in the Hard Shell Tower?

00:15:47.046 --> 00:15:48.981
We haven't heard anything
about sis in a while

00:15:49.014 --> 00:15:52.117
and it's really starting
to bug me-fa-so-la!

00:15:52.151 --> 00:15:53.819
How did you feel
about the Straw Hats?

00:15:53.852 --> 00:15:55.988
'Cause I didn't think
they were bad people.

00:15:56.021 --> 00:15:58.324
Madam Sharley said that
they'd destroy the country,

00:15:58.357 --> 00:16:02.227
but so far, they seem like
the least of our worries.

00:16:02.261 --> 00:16:04.263
They have caused
their share of trouble,

00:16:04.296 --> 00:16:06.098
but they may be victims, too.

00:16:06.131 --> 00:16:09.768
That's what I think.
Straw Hat's Jimbei's friend,

00:16:09.802 --> 00:16:12.638
and the mermaids didn't
have a problem with them.

00:16:12.671 --> 00:16:15.641
And frankly, their
judgment is rarely wrong.

00:16:15.674 --> 00:16:17.409
Agreed, but this is not the time

00:16:17.443 --> 00:16:19.912
nor the place to
ponder such questions!

00:16:19.945 --> 00:16:22.948
Right. We need
to focus-so-la-ti-do!

00:16:22.982 --> 00:16:25.818
[FUKABOSHI] Summon every soldier
that the country has to offer!

00:16:25.851 --> 00:16:28.153
We're going to save
our king at any cost!

00:16:28.187 --> 00:16:30.022
[AMMO KNIGHTS]
Yes, sir!

00:16:30.055 --> 00:16:31.623
[IKAROS grunts]

00:16:31.657 --> 00:16:33.058
[NARRATOR]
At Fishverly Hills

00:16:33.092 --> 00:16:34.793
in the northeast
part of the island.

00:16:34.827 --> 00:16:38.364
[SEA BEAR A snarls]

00:16:39.298 --> 00:16:40.466
He's too tough!

00:16:40.499 --> 00:16:42.601
Damn it! We shouldn't
be having this much trouble

00:16:42.634 --> 00:16:44.903
fighting against
just one sea monster!

00:16:44.937 --> 00:16:47.606
But then again, it seems
something is amiss.

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:50.376
[SEA BEAR A snarls]

00:16:50.409 --> 00:16:53.345
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE Q laughs]
Look at these fools.

00:16:53.379 --> 00:16:55.948
Serves them right! All right,
Sea King, keep it up!

00:16:55.981 --> 00:16:57.850
--[SEA BEAR A roars]
--[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES yell]

00:16:59.018 --> 00:17:02.421
Ahh! The Energy Steroids
are makin' him crazy!

00:17:02.454 --> 00:17:04.423
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE R]
Hey! Calm down, Sea Bear!

00:17:04.456 --> 00:17:07.192
That's enough! The soldiers
are barely alive.

00:17:07.226 --> 00:17:08.927
Our job here is done!

00:17:08.961 --> 00:17:11.697
Use this! Sea Kings
don't like fire.

00:17:11.730 --> 00:17:12.998
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE R]
Stay back!

00:17:18.337 --> 00:17:20.305
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE R grunts]

00:17:20.339 --> 00:17:22.408
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE R]
Uhh...

00:17:23.442 --> 00:17:25.644
[IKAROS]
Roar!

00:17:25.677 --> 00:17:26.311
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES]
Huh?

00:17:26.345 --> 00:17:30.182
[IKAROS]
Roar!

00:17:30.215 --> 00:17:31.383
What the...?

00:17:31.417 --> 00:17:33.719
I don't think his arms are
supposed to bend back like that!

00:17:33.752 --> 00:17:35.754
He must be under
some kind of a curse!

00:17:35.788 --> 00:17:39.058
You idiot! Put out
that fire right away! Hii!

00:17:39.091 --> 00:17:39.992
Hot! Hot! Hot!

00:17:40.025 --> 00:17:42.394
Huh? You said
something about fire?

00:17:42.428 --> 00:17:44.563
[IKAROS yells]

00:17:44.596 --> 00:17:47.099
What are you trying to do,
cook up some smoked squid?

00:17:47.132 --> 00:17:48.500
You think we'd eat you?

00:17:48.534 --> 00:17:49.968
Oh, the fire.

00:17:51.270 --> 00:17:52.438
You were trying to roast me

00:17:52.471 --> 00:17:54.506
and have me with
a glass of sakÃ©. Hii.

00:17:54.540 --> 00:17:56.408
When I recover, I'll kill you!

00:17:56.442 --> 00:17:58.477
Who'd wanna do that?
You're crazy!

00:17:58.510 --> 00:18:00.412
Oh, sorry, sir.

00:18:00.446 --> 00:18:02.981
Careful. I heard about
how one of Ikaros's

00:18:03.015 --> 00:18:05.050
best friends was a giant squid.

00:18:05.084 --> 00:18:07.319
One day he swam
too close to the sun.

00:18:07.352 --> 00:18:10.022
Before you know it,
he was a giant dried squid!

00:18:10.055 --> 00:18:13.092
That's why Ikaros freaks
out when he sees fire.

00:18:13.125 --> 00:18:17.162
I'm sorry, Daidalos!

00:18:17.196 --> 00:18:18.430
But if he's a Fishman,

00:18:18.464 --> 00:18:20.132
he doesn't have anything
to worry about.

00:18:20.165 --> 00:18:21.867
[IKAROS]
Daida.

00:18:21.900 --> 00:18:24.069
[IKAROS sobs]

00:18:27.072 --> 00:18:28.474
[IKAROS grunts]

00:18:28.507 --> 00:18:29.708
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE R groans]

00:18:29.741 --> 00:18:31.543
No more fire! Got me? Hii?

00:18:31.577 --> 00:18:32.411
Oh, no!

00:18:32.444 --> 00:18:34.613
That Dried Squid
Spear is dangerous!

00:18:34.646 --> 00:18:36.415
It turns back
into a normal squid

00:18:36.448 --> 00:18:39.184
by sucking all the fluid
out of anyone it strikes!

00:18:39.218 --> 00:18:41.553
That guy's as good as jerky!

00:18:42.855 --> 00:18:45.424
[IKAROS]
Ika!

00:18:45.457 --> 00:18:50.129
Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika, Ika...

00:18:50.162 --> 00:18:51.497
Wow! That's rough!

00:18:51.530 --> 00:18:53.932
First he got dried out,
and then this happens?

00:18:53.966 --> 00:18:56.635
'Kay, Boss Ikaros!
I think he's had enough!

00:18:56.668 --> 00:18:57.970
Isn't it about time we start

00:18:58.003 --> 00:18:59.905
making our way
to Conchcorde Plaza?

00:18:59.938 --> 00:19:02.474
Muhi! You're right!

00:19:02.508 --> 00:19:04.143
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATE U]
It's too late for that guy.

00:19:04.176 --> 00:19:05.477
Leave him here.

00:19:05.511 --> 00:19:09.381
Minister! You need
to see this, sir!

00:19:09.414 --> 00:19:11.550
[MINISTER OF THE RIGHT gasps]

00:19:11.583 --> 00:19:14.019
Hordy. Is that him up there?

00:19:14.052 --> 00:19:15.087
[AMMO KNIGHT B]
I don't see Hordy,

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:17.322
but I do see other men
from the Fishman District!

00:19:17.356 --> 00:19:20.159
[AMMO KNIGHT D] They must be
heading to the Conchcorde Plaza!

00:19:20.192 --> 00:19:21.894
Damn those bastards!

00:19:21.927 --> 00:19:24.496
No way! They still have
King Neptune hostage!

00:19:24.530 --> 00:19:27.199
You can't let them beat you!

00:19:27.232 --> 00:19:27.900
[NEPTUNE grunts]

00:19:27.933 --> 00:19:29.835
Please do something!

00:19:29.868 --> 00:19:33.071
Great Knight,
your people need you!

00:19:33.105 --> 00:19:37.442
[NEPTUNE] I'm no Great Knight,
not anymore. Look at me!

00:19:37.476 --> 00:19:41.113
I can't even save
my poor citizens.

00:19:41.146 --> 00:19:43.115
Please hang in there!

00:19:43.148 --> 00:19:44.816
[MINISTER OF THE RIGHT]
What good is a king's army

00:19:44.850 --> 00:19:47.553
if it can't even protect
the king it serves?

00:19:47.586 --> 00:19:49.955
We're an embarrassment
to this country.

00:19:49.988 --> 00:19:53.725
Sir Ikaros! Just two hours
left till the execution!

00:19:53.759 --> 00:19:55.794
Come with us to
Conchcorde Plaza!

00:19:55.827 --> 00:19:57.896
[IKAROS]
What happened to Captain Hordy?

00:19:57.930 --> 00:19:59.331
Is he not with you?

00:19:59.364 --> 00:20:01.934
Why isn't he talking
to me directly-hii?

00:20:01.967 --> 00:20:03.001
Huh?

00:20:03.035 --> 00:20:04.736
About that...

00:20:04.770 --> 00:20:06.572
Huh?

00:20:06.605 --> 00:20:09.541
[HORDY gasping]

00:20:09.575 --> 00:20:11.476
[NEPTUNE]
That drug enhances your strength

00:20:11.510 --> 00:20:13.612
at the cost of your lifespan.

00:20:13.645 --> 00:20:16.915
You shouldn't have taken
it in the first place.

00:20:16.949 --> 00:20:19.051
[HORDY]
Shut up!

00:20:19.084 --> 00:20:20.886
Captain Hordy was injured!

00:20:20.919 --> 00:20:22.788
The human pirate
swordsman cut him

00:20:22.821 --> 00:20:24.723
and the gash is
too painful to bear!

00:20:24.756 --> 00:20:27.192
[IKAROS] Injured?
The Captain got injured?

00:20:27.226 --> 00:20:28.694
His body wouldn't stop hurting,

00:20:28.727 --> 00:20:32.030
so he kept taking Energy
Steroids to help kill the pain!

00:20:32.064 --> 00:20:34.900
[HORDY gasping]

00:20:34.933 --> 00:20:36.134
Now he's messed up.

00:20:36.168 --> 00:20:38.637
We told him to stop, but he
wouldn't listen to anyone!

00:20:38.670 --> 00:20:42.374
[HORDY groaning]

00:20:42.407 --> 00:20:44.610
No, Captain Hordy!

00:20:46.178 --> 00:20:49.248
Can't breathe. I can't--

00:20:49.281 --> 00:20:52.317
Feel like I'm gonna explode!

00:20:52.351 --> 00:20:54.987
Muhi! It's just as I suspected.

00:20:55.020 --> 00:20:58.090
The drug's side effects
are bad enough to kill you.

00:21:00.592 --> 00:21:05.597
[HORDY screaming]

00:21:31.690 --> 00:21:32.991
[NEPTUNE]
Hmm?

00:21:36.194 --> 00:21:38.130
Whoa, something's wrong.

00:21:44.703 --> 00:21:46.138
[whimpers]

00:21:46.171 --> 00:21:49.374
[SEA BEAR A whimpering]

00:21:49.408 --> 00:21:51.076
What's wrong with
you now, Sea Bear?

00:21:51.109 --> 00:21:52.844
I think he must be afraid!

00:21:52.878 --> 00:21:54.212
But all these sea
monsters have been

00:21:54.246 --> 00:21:57.649
under Captain Hordy's control
for a really long time now!

00:21:57.683 --> 00:22:00.252
I don't know what would
spook him so much.

00:22:06.058 --> 00:22:07.926
Uh, is that you, Captain?

00:22:07.959 --> 00:22:09.995
You doin' okay there?

00:22:10.028 --> 00:22:14.132
But of course.
And why wouldn't I be?

00:22:21.173 --> 00:22:23.608
He's alive,
but something changed.

00:22:28.714 --> 00:22:29.915
[HORDY]
Huh?

00:22:30.916 --> 00:22:32.918
[chuckles]

00:22:32.951 --> 00:22:36.021
Some of Neptune's
soldiers are still alive.

00:22:38.523 --> 00:22:39.157
[ALL gasp]

00:22:39.191 --> 00:22:40.859
Water Shot!

00:22:42.461 --> 00:22:45.130
[AMMO KNIGHTS scream]

00:22:49.568 --> 00:22:51.336
[NEW FISHMAN PIRATES gasp]

00:22:59.945 --> 00:23:05.951
[cackling]

00:23:14.893 --> 00:23:16.428
[NARRATOR]
Neptune's army is crushed

00:23:16.461 --> 00:23:19.664
by the overwhelming might of
the newly-transformed Hordy.

00:23:19.698 --> 00:23:20.899
The people's last hope

00:23:20.932 --> 00:23:23.635
lies in the three princes
of the Ryugu Kingdom.

00:23:23.668 --> 00:23:24.703
Rushing to the scene,

00:23:24.736 --> 00:23:27.072
they quickly battle
Hordy's sea monsters,

00:23:27.105 --> 00:23:29.474
but his crewmates have
a dirty trick up their sleeves

00:23:29.508 --> 00:23:32.210
that could turn the
tables once again.

00:23:32.244 --> 00:23:33.879
[LUFFY]
On the next One Piece!

00:23:33.912 --> 00:23:36.848
"The Battle is on!
At Conchcorde Plaza!"

00:23:36.882 --> 00:23:39.451
I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

